-- Javier Pano appointed CFO at Caixabank
-- By Sonya Dowsett
-- Fri Jul 11, 2014 10:38AM EDT
-- None



MADRID, July 11 (Reuters) - Spanish bank Caixabank <CABK.MC> said on Friday it had appointed Javier Pano as its new chief financial officer as part of a restructuring following the departure of former chief executive Juan Maria Nin last month. [ID:nL6N0PB4OI]

